to the "me" I was before, the "me" you want.

17
00:01:30,580 --> 00:01:32,260
That's not true!

18
00:01:33,360 --> 00:01:35,550
Natsumi...

19
00:01:51,590 --> 00:01:54,310
I'm not going to give up!

20
